quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,43,"Nombe mu (abali ja) achina Samuda (muŵele mwana chilosyo cha ipotesi), pandema jaŵasalilidwe kuti: “Sengwagani kwakandaŵi kannono.”"
  51,44,"Ni ŵalikwesisye kuleka lilamusi lya M’mbuje gwao (Allah), ni wakwembekenye n’gumilo (wa ipotesi) aku ali nkulola."
  51,45,"Ni nganakombola kwima (kuti atile), soni nganaŵa ŵanti nikulikulupusya (achimisyene)."
  52,34,"Basi ayiche najo abali janti mpela jalakweji (Qur’an), naŵaga jamanjao akuŵecheta yakuona."
  52,35,"Kapena ŵagumbidwe mwangali chilichose (chakwagumba), kapena ŵanganyao ni ŵaŵaligumbile (achimisyene)?"
  52,36,"Kapena ŵanganyao ni ŵaŵagumbile mawunde ni mataka? (Ngwamba), nambo kuti ngakusimichisya (ya ilagasyo ya Allah)."
  53,28,"Ni nganakola ŵanganyao pa yalakweyo umanyilisi uliose, ngakukuya ikaŵeje liganichisya, sano liganichisya lyangakamuchisya chilichose pa yakuona."
  53,29,"Basi munnekaani ajula jwaachitundumalile chikumbusyo Chetu (Qur’an), ni ngajukusaka ikaŵeje umi wa duniya."
  53,30,"Chele ni chipelela chao cha umanyilisi. Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni ŵaakummanyilila jwaapoteele kuleka litala Lyakwe, nambo soni ni ŵaakummanyilila jwajongweche."
  54,19,"Chisimu Uwwe twatumichisye mbungo jakusisima nnope mu lisiku lyachitapani chakwendelechela."
  54,20,"Jaliji nkwachuŵa ŵandu (kuja nao mwinani, kaneka nikwagwichisya pasi mwakwapitikusya) nti chisawu ŵanganyao mapata ga itela ya tende yechuŵidwe."
  54,21,"Ana ilagasyo Yangu yaliji uli kwisa soni itetelo Yangu?"
  55,13,"Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)?"
  55,14,"Jwagumbile mundu (Adam) kuumila mwilongo lyakulilaga mpela liigeleesya."
  55,15,"Sano majini ni ŵagagumbile kuumila m’malamba ga moto gangali lyosi."
  56,4,"Ndema jalichitenganyika litaka kutenganyika kwamachili."
  56,5,"Matumbi ni kusyajidwa-syajidwa."
  56,6,"Ni kuŵa luwundu lyakuwululusyidwa."